# Summary
Adapty is an all-in-one subscription monetization platform that integrates with Amplitude to send user behavior data, enabling analysis of in-app purchases and subscriptions. The integration requires copying your Amplitude API key to Adapty's dashboard and configuring the SDK to properly map user IDs between platforms.

